{"formatVersion":"1","manifest":{"sourceId":"mirabai-hi","displayName":"मीराबाई भजन","displayNameEnglish":"Mirabai Bhajans — Hindi","version":"1.0","language":"Hindi","languageCode":"hi","script":"Devanagari","isRTL":false,"transliterationAvailable":false,"edition":"Public Domain & Curated / Hindi Wikiquote","primaryCategory":"Philosophy & Spirituality","subcategory":"Hindi Wisdom","type":"quotes","browseOrder":"sequence","supportsRandom":true,"supportsBrowse":true,"groupingLevels":[],"groupingLabels":[],"sortPriority":52,"contentRating":"devotional","audienceTags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:devotion","theme:love"],"itemCount":33,"dataPath":"Data/Collections/Mirabai_Hindi.json"},"data":[{"id":"mirabai-hi-0001","text":"मेरे तो गिरिधर गोपाल दूसरो न कोई।\nजाके सिर मोर मुकुट मेरो पति सोई।","author":"Mirabai Bhajans — Hindi","source":"मीराबाई भजन (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th-16th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:devotion","theme:love"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"mirabai-hi-0002","text":"पायो जी मैंने राम रतन धन पायो।\nवस्तु अमोलक दी मेरे सतगुरु किरपा कर अपनायो।","author":"Mirabai Bhajans — Hindi","source":"मीराबाई भजन (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th-16th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:devotion","theme:love"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"mirabai-hi-0003","text":"हरि तुम हरो जन की पीर।\nद्रौपदी की लाज राखी तुम बढायो चीर।","author":"Mirabai Bhajans — Hindi","source":"मीराबाई भजन (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th-16th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:devotion","theme:love"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"mirabai-hi-0004","text":"चलो मन गंगा यमुना तीर।\nगंगा यमुना निर्मल पानी, शीतल होत शरीर।","author":"Mirabai Bhajans — Hindi","source":"मीराबाई भजन (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th-16th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:devotion","theme:love"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"mirabai-hi-0005","text":"जो तुम तोड़ो पिया मैं नहीं तोड़ूं।\nतोड़ूं तो जग बनस जाय, पिया बिन जीवन छोड़ूं।","author":"Mirabai Bhajans — Hindi","source":"मीराबाई भजन (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th-16th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:devotion","theme:love"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"mirabai-hi-0006","text":"आज रंग है री मना रंग है।\nमेरे महबूब के घर रंग है।","author":"Mirabai Bhajans — Hindi","source":"मीराबाई भजन (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th-16th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:devotion","theme:love"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"mirabai-hi-0007","text":"बसो मेरे नैनन में नंदलाल।\nमोहनी मूरति सांवरि सूरति, नैना बने विशाल।","author":"Mirabai Bhajans — Hindi","source":"मीराबाई भजन (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th-16th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:devotion","theme:love"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"mirabai-hi-0008","text":"श्याम मनोहर देखन को आयो।\nगोकुल गांव फिरो वन-वन, मन हरि लीला लायो।","author":"Mirabai Bhajans — Hindi","source":"मीराबाई भजन (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th-16th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:devotion","theme:love"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"mirabai-hi-0009","text":"मीरा के प्रभु गिरिधर नागर, सहज मिले अविनाशी।\nसाध-संगति में बैठ-बैठ कर, लोक-लाज सब खोई।","author":"Mirabai Bhajans — Hindi","source":"मीराबाई भजन (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th-16th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:devotion","theme:love"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"mirabai-hi-0010","text":"माई री मैं तो लियो गोविंदो मोल।\nकोई कहे छानो कोई कहे सांचो, लियो मैं परखि ढोल।","author":"Mirabai Bhajans — Hindi","source":"मीराबाई भजन (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th-16th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:devotion","theme:love"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"mirabai-hi-0011","text":"जोगी मत जा मत जा मत जा।\nतेरे जोग में मारा मन मेरा, तू मत जा।","author":"Mirabai Bhajans — Hindi","source":"मीराबाई भजन (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th-16th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:devotion","theme:love"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"mirabai-hi-0012","text":"सखी मेरे राम की रुचि बड़ी।\nराम कही सौतन को न डरूं, लगी अब नेह की गाड़ी।","author":"Mirabai Bhajans — Hindi","source":"मीराबाई भजन (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th-16th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:devotion","theme:love"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"mirabai-hi-0013","text":"राम बिना दुःख पाए नाथ।\nजस जल बिन मीन दुखित जैसे, जब सो दर्शन पाय।","author":"Mirabai Bhajans — Hindi","source":"मीराबाई भजन (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th-16th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:devotion","theme:love"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"mirabai-hi-0014","text":"दर्शन दो घनश्याम नाथ मोरी।\nबाट जोहत नैन भये चकोरी।","author":"Mirabai Bhajans — Hindi","source":"मीराबाई भजन (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th-16th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:devotion","theme:love"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"mirabai-hi-0015","text":"जो रंगे सो रंगे मन माहीं।\nमीरां के प्रभु गिरिधर नागर बिन मिले चैन नाहीं।","author":"Mirabai Bhajans — Hindi","source":"मीराबाई भजन (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th-16th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:devotion","theme:love"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"mirabai-hi-0016","text":"मेरी लगन लागी श्री राम चरणन में।\nदिन रात भजन करूं मैं प्रेम से मन में।","author":"Mirabai Bhajans — Hindi","source":"मीराबाई भजन (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th-16th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:devotion","theme:love"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"mirabai-hi-0017","text":"हे री मैं तो प्रेम दीवानी मेरा दर्द न जाने कोय।\nदर्द की मारी बन-बन डोलूं, बैद मिला नहिं कोय।","author":"Mirabai Bhajans — Hindi","source":"मीराबाई भजन (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th-16th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:devotion","theme:love"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"mirabai-hi-0018","text":"घूंघट के पट खोल रे, तोहे पिया मिलेंगे।\nघट-घट में वो साईं रमता, कटुक वचन मत बोल रे।","author":"Mirabai Bhajans — Hindi","source":"मीराबाई भजन (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th-16th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:devotion","theme:love"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"mirabai-hi-0019","text":"अब तो माधव मोहि उर लाव।\nनहिं तो तुम बिन कैसे जीऊं, तुम्हरे आसरे आव।","author":"Mirabai Bhajans — Hindi","source":"मीराबाई भजन (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th-16th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:devotion","theme:love"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"mirabai-hi-0020","text":"तन रंगो री रंगो मन मेरो।\nहरि रंग रंगी भई मीरां बाई, जनम जनम को फेरो।","author":"Mirabai Bhajans — Hindi","source":"मीराबाई भजन (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th-16th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:devotion","theme:love"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"mirabai-hi-0021","text":"कृष्ण कन्हैया लाल की जय।\nवृंदावन बिहारी की जय।","author":"Mirabai Bhajans — Hindi","source":"मीराबाई भजन (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th-16th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:devotion","theme:love"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"mirabai-hi-0022","text":"प्रभु जी तुम चंदन हम पानी।\nजाकी अंग-अंग बास समानी।","author":"Mirabai Bhajans — Hindi","source":"मीराबाई भजन (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th-16th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:devotion","theme:love"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"mirabai-hi-0023","text":"मेरा मन मंदिर नंदलाल।\nप्रीत की रासि भई निर्मल, भयो उजागर ख्याल।","author":"Mirabai Bhajans — Hindi","source":"मीराबाई भजन (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th-16th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:devotion","theme:love"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"mirabai-hi-0024","text":"निस दिन बरसत नैन हमारे।\nसदा रहत पावस ऋतु हम पर, प्रभु बिन दुख के मारे।","author":"Mirabai Bhajans — Hindi","source":"मीराबाई भजन (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th-16th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:devotion","theme:love"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"mirabai-hi-0025","text":"मुझे चाकर राखो जी राखो जी।\nगिरिधर की चाकरी करूं मैं, नाम जपत मन लाखो जी।","author":"Mirabai Bhajans — Hindi","source":"मीराबाई भजन (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th-16th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:devotion","theme:love"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"mirabai-hi-0026","text":"माला जपत, जाप मन जपत।\nहरि नाम बिन कैसे रहूं, पल-पल जियो मन तरपत।","author":"Mirabai Bhajans — Hindi","source":"मीराबाई भजन (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th-16th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:devotion","theme:love"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"mirabai-hi-0027","text":"वृंदावन की कुंज गलिन में।\nश्याम मिले मन मेरो भटकत, प्रेम-मगन दिन रैन में।","author":"Mirabai Bhajans — Hindi","source":"मीराबाई भजन (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th-16th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:devotion","theme:love"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"mirabai-hi-0028","text":"रात चिंतन करूं मैं नित्य नाम।\nदिन उठ देखूं जब से हरि-धाम।","author":"Mirabai Bhajans — Hindi","source":"मीराबाई भजन (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th-16th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:devotion","theme:love"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"mirabai-hi-0029","text":"आवो री सखी मिल गायें।\nगोविंद की लीला गुण गायें।","author":"Mirabai Bhajans — Hindi","source":"मीराबाई भजन (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th-16th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:devotion","theme:love"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"mirabai-hi-0030","text":"जीवन में हरि भक्ति बड़ी।\nमीरां को प्रभु मिले, जीवन-नैया पड़ी।","author":"Mirabai Bhajans — Hindi","source":"मीराबाई भजन (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th-16th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:devotion","theme:love"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"mirabai-hi-0031","text":"जन्म जन्म की प्रीत निभानी।\nमीरां के मन बसे गोपाल, यही मेरी कहानी।","author":"Mirabai Bhajans — Hindi","source":"मीराबाई भजन (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th-16th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:devotion","theme:love"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"mirabai-hi-0032","text":"कोई कहे पागल कोई कहे दीवानी।\nमीरां को सब कुछ हरि, यही उनकी रवानी।","author":"Mirabai Bhajans — Hindi","source":"मीराबाई भजन (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th-16th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:devotion","theme:love"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."},{"id":"mirabai-hi-0033","text":"दासी मीरां लाल गिरिधारी।\nकरत कृपा सहज अविकारी।","author":"Mirabai Bhajans — Hindi","source":"मीराबाई भजन (Braj Bhasha, Public Domain ~15th-16th c.)","tags":["language:hi","script:devanagari","tradition:bhakti","tradition:hindi","theme:devotion","theme:love"],"isProverb":false,"isVerified":true,"verificationNote":"Verified via Hindi Wikiquote / curated public-domain source."}]}